    "question_id" : 29241640,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just to say 16.04, I'm running </p>\n\n<pre><code>sudo apt-get install lib32z1 lib32ncurses5 libbz2-1.0:i386 lib32stdc++6\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>seems to work on a vanilla install after installing oracle-jdk-8</p>\n"
